properties.Name: Survey
properties.Description:
A planned investigation that consists of questions or queries presented to an Individual.

A Survey consists of one or more Questions.   A Question may be asked in one or more Surveys.

The analysis of responses provides the product-provider with a basis upon which to make business decisions.

The results of the same questions can then be compared over time or compared in various contexts.

Columns.Name: SurveyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Survey.

Columns.Name: SurveyStartDate
Columns.Description: The "period" start date of the Survey.

Columns.Name: SurveyEndDate
Columns.Description: The "period" end date of the Survey.

Columns.Name: SurveyDescription
Columns.Description:
The description of the Survey.

This would also be a good place to describe the objectives to be addressed by the Survey and detail measurement parameters that apply to the Survey.

Columns.Name: SurveyNote
Columns.Description: A comment, note or description regarding the Survey,

Columns.Name: SurveyTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Survey Type.
